comments: Belgium - peaked at #1 in Flanders. Also peaked at #6 in Wallonia three weeks later. #1 in The Netherlands for three weeks in 1975. Furthermore it reached #1 in Austria, Finland, Flanders, Germany, Norway, Sweden and Switzerland and it also topped the charts of New Zealand and South Africa. In the US it became a #1 hit on the Billboard Easy Listening Singles chart on 14 February 1976 (becoming that chart's overall #1 song for 1976), peaked at #26 on the Billboard Hot 100 and reached #33 on the Billboard Hot Country Singles chart. In Australia it reached #2 and #10 in Canada and the UK. The single sold over two million copies worldwide.
